## Attribution

This project was created as a demonstration of enterprise WordPress development
skills for the rtCamp Associate Software Engineer application. It showcases
modern PHP development, WordPress expertise, and enterprise-scale thinking.

The project addresses real challenges faced by WordPress agencies managing
multiple high-traffic client websites, demonstrating practical solutions for
plugin performance monitoring, security scanning, and client reporting.
